(8, 1, '2014-12-07 16:15:36', '2014-12-07 08:15:36', '2014年被认为是AngularJS之年，现在是时候总结一下2013年的AngularJS优秀学习资源，希望能帮助你迎头赶上。只有最好的文章才能榜上有名。\r\n\r\n下面是 Aneesha Bakharia 整理的精选内容：\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader0">AngularJS新手学习</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://code-like-a-poem.blogspot.com.au/2013/03/behold-angularjs-is-here-about.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">有想法的菜鸟看过来——这就是AngularJS！！</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://net.tutsplus.com/tutorials/javascript-ajax/5-awesome-angularjs-features/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS 的五个超酷特性</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/angularjs-tutorial/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">30分钟学会AngularJS（AngularJS教程）</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://fastandfluid.com/publicdownloads/AngularJSIn60MinutesIsh_DanWahlin_May2013.pdf" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">60分钟学AngularJS （PDF版，作者Dan Wahlin）</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://joelhooks.com/blog/2013/04/24/modeling-data-and-state-in-your-angularjs-application/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">在AngularJS 应用中为你的数据和状态建模</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.benlesh.com/2013/02/angularjs-creating-service-with-http.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使用 $http 创建 Service</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://blog.revolunet.com/blog/2013/06/01/starting-with-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">学习AngularJS五步曲</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://weblogs.asp.net/dwahlin/archive/2013/05/22/dynamically-loading-controllers-and-views-with-angularjs-and-requirejs.aspx" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">用RequireJS和AngularJS动态加载Controllers和Views</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://trochette.github.io/Angular-Design-Patterns-Best-Practices/#/proven" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">高级设计模式和最佳实践</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://flippinawesome.org/2013/08/05/animating-with-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS 动画</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://weblogs.asp.net/dwahlin/archive/2013/08/16/using-an-angularjs-factory-to-interact-with-a-restful-service.aspx" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">U使用AngularJS Factory 和 RESTful 服务进行交互</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.davidsalter.com/2013/08/16/using-angular-dot-js-factories-to-get-remote-data/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">U使用AngularJS Factories获取远程数据</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.sitepoint.com/10-reasons-use-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">为何应该使用AngularJS的十个理由</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://blog.xebia.com/2013/09/01/differences-between-providers-in-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS中的Providers(Provide, Factory, Service)之间的区别</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.kidsil.net/2013/09/filtering-with-angularjs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS过滤器（Filter）</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://blog.artlogic.com/2013/03/06/angularjs-for-jquery-developers/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">jQuery程序员眼中的AngularJS</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://wintellect.com/blogs/jlikness/10-reasons-web-developers-should-learn-angularjs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Web开发者应该学习AngularJS的十个理由</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://kirkbushell.me/when-to-use-directives-controllers-or-services-in-angular/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">在AngularJS中何时应该使用Directives，Controllers或者Service</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://blog.thousandeyes.com/creating-extensible-widgets-part-1-jquery-to-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">30秒，从jQuery到AngularJS</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.ng-newsletter.com/posts/angular-on-mobile.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">移动端Angular权威指南</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader1">AngularJS应用实践</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://weblogs.asp.net/dwahlin/archive/2013/10/25/learning-angularjs-by-example-the-customer-manager-application.aspx" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">通过实例学习AngularJS：客户管理程序</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.recursiverobot.com/post/53767548784/angularjs-with-indexeddb-using-a-helper-library" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS with IndexedDB using a helper library</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://icelab.com.au/articles/levelling-up-with-angularjs-building-a-reusable-click-to-edit-directive/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS进阶：做一个可重用的“点击编辑”指令</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://responsiblysourced.wordpress.com/2013/07/08/reactive-real-time-log-search-with-play-akka-angularjs-and-elasticsearch/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">基于Play、Akka、AngularJS和Elasticsearch的实时响应日志查询</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://www.firebase.com/blog/2013-07-16-build-your-own-feed-reader.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">还在想念Googler Reader？使用Firebase和AngularJS做自己的阅读器</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://abou-kone.com/2013/07/17/developing-a-mobile-app-with-phonegap-angularjs-and-expressjs-part-i/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使用Phonegap、AngularJS和ExpressJS创建一个移动应用（第一部分）</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://matthiasnehlsen.com/blog/2013/08/13/birdwatch-angularjs-elasticsearch-play/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">BirdWatch v0.2：基于AngularJS，ElasticSearch和Play框架的Tweet流分析</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.opensourceconnections.com/2013/08/25/instant-search-with-solr-and-angular/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">基于Solr和AngularJS的即时搜索</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/amirrajan/sortis" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Sorties：Twitter重度用户的客户端，也是程序员开发基于twitter程序的跳板</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://timothy.userapp.io/post/64117882900/customizable-twitter-timeline-for-angularjs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS打造的可定制的Twitter Timeline</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://seanhess.github.io/2013/10/14/angularjs-directive-design.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使AngularJS指令设计变得简单</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader2">AngularJS指令</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.phloxblog.in/jquery-plugin-angular-js-directive-clean-html-approach/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">为jQuery插件创建AngularJS指令</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.phloxblog.in/d3-js-angular-directive/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">为D3.js柱状图创建AngularJS指令</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.directiv.es/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">www.directiv.es：一个AngularJS指令资源库</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/agrublev/Angular-localStorage" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS 本地存储</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://twofuckingdevelopers.com/2013/08/videogular-an-html5-video-player-for-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Videogular：AngularJS打造的HTML5视频播放器</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://jmdobry.github.io/angular-cache/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS 缓存</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://angular-ui.github.io/bootstrap/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Twitter Bootstrap的AngularJS指令</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/wesleyhales/angular-charts" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Angular的图表指令(directive)和服务(service)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://modernjavascript.blogspot.com.au/2013/10/angularjs-table-sort.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">表格排序</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader3">AngularJS 游戏</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.sitepoint.com/angularjs-tutorial-build-an-app-using-directives-and-data-binding/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">CoffeeScript写的一个OX小游戏</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/callmehiphop/mario-cards" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">超级马里奥卡片翻转游戏</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader4">AngularJS开发流程和测试</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.youtube.com/watchv=UYVcY9EJcRs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS测试策略[Youtube视频]</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.portlandwebworks.com/blog/combining-yeoman-angularjs-and-cordova-mobile-development" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使用Yeoman，AngularJS和Cordova做移动应用开发</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.youtube.com/watchv=eUmDDxrvqSs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">用Angular和Yeoman开发Chrome应用简介[Youtube视频]</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.phloxblog.in/angular-js-tests-jasmine/#.UfzX3pI3CSp" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">用Jasmine测试AngularJS应用</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.yearofmoo.com/2013/01/full-spectrum-testing-with-angularjs-and-karma.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使用Karma对AngularJS应用做全方位的测试</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/m7r/grunt-ngdocs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使用一个Grunt task创建AngularJS文档</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/joshdmiller/ng-boilerplate" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">ng-boilerplate：一个AngularJS新项目的样板项目</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/angular/angularjs-batarang" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Chrome的AngularJS监控插件</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://weblogs.asp.net/dwahlin/archive/2013/08/30/using-the-angularjs-package-for-sublime-text.aspx" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">在Sublime Text中使用AngularJS包</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader5">AngularJS书籍（英文）</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.manning.com/bford/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS实战</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://leanpub.com/ng-book" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS入门指南</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://www.packtpub.com/angularjs-web-application-development/book" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">精通AngularJS Web应用开发</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '2014年Angularjs学习资源精选', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '2014%e5%b9%b4angularjs%e5%ad%a6%e4%b9%a0%e8%b5%84%e6%ba%90%e7%b2%be%e9%80%89', '', '', '2014-12-07 16:15:36', '2014-12-07 08:15:36', '', 0, 'http://ngionic.com/?p=8', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(9, 1, '2014-12-07 16:15:36', '2014-12-07 08:15:36', '2014年被认为是AngularJS之年，现在是时候总结一下2013年的AngularJS优秀学习资源，希望能帮助你迎头赶上。只有最好的文章才能榜上有名。\r\n\r\n下面是 Aneesha Bakharia 整理的精选内容：\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader0">AngularJS新手学习</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://code-like-a-poem.blogspot.com.au/2013/03/behold-angularjs-is-here-about.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">有想法的菜鸟看过来——这就是AngularJS！！</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://net.tutsplus.com/tutorials/javascript-ajax/5-awesome-angularjs-features/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS 的五个超酷特性</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/angularjs-tutorial/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">30分钟学会AngularJS（AngularJS教程）</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://fastandfluid.com/publicdownloads/AngularJSIn60MinutesIsh_DanWahlin_May2013.pdf" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">60分钟学AngularJS （PDF版，作者Dan Wahlin）</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://joelhooks.com/blog/2013/04/24/modeling-data-and-state-in-your-angularjs-application/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">在AngularJS 应用中为你的数据和状态建模</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.benlesh.com/2013/02/angularjs-creating-service-with-http.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使用 $http 创建 Service</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://blog.revolunet.com/blog/2013/06/01/starting-with-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">学习AngularJS五步曲</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://weblogs.asp.net/dwahlin/archive/2013/05/22/dynamically-loading-controllers-and-views-with-angularjs-and-requirejs.aspx" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">用RequireJS和AngularJS动态加载Controllers和Views</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://trochette.github.io/Angular-Design-Patterns-Best-Practices/#/proven" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">高级设计模式和最佳实践</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://flippinawesome.org/2013/08/05/animating-with-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS 动画</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://weblogs.asp.net/dwahlin/archive/2013/08/16/using-an-angularjs-factory-to-interact-with-a-restful-service.aspx" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">U使用AngularJS Factory 和 RESTful 服务进行交互</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.davidsalter.com/2013/08/16/using-angular-dot-js-factories-to-get-remote-data/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">U使用AngularJS Factories获取远程数据</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.sitepoint.com/10-reasons-use-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">为何应该使用AngularJS的十个理由</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://blog.xebia.com/2013/09/01/differences-between-providers-in-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS中的Providers(Provide, Factory, Service)之间的区别</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.kidsil.net/2013/09/filtering-with-angularjs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS过滤器（Filter）</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://blog.artlogic.com/2013/03/06/angularjs-for-jquery-developers/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">jQuery程序员眼中的AngularJS</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://wintellect.com/blogs/jlikness/10-reasons-web-developers-should-learn-angularjs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Web开发者应该学习AngularJS的十个理由</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://kirkbushell.me/when-to-use-directives-controllers-or-services-in-angular/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">在AngularJS中何时应该使用Directives，Controllers或者Service</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://blog.thousandeyes.com/creating-extensible-widgets-part-1-jquery-to-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">30秒，从jQuery到AngularJS</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.ng-newsletter.com/posts/angular-on-mobile.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">移动端Angular权威指南</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader1">AngularJS应用实践</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://weblogs.asp.net/dwahlin/archive/2013/10/25/learning-angularjs-by-example-the-customer-manager-application.aspx" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">通过实例学习AngularJS：客户管理程序</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.recursiverobot.com/post/53767548784/angularjs-with-indexeddb-using-a-helper-library" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS with IndexedDB using a helper library</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://icelab.com.au/articles/levelling-up-with-angularjs-building-a-reusable-click-to-edit-directive/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS进阶：做一个可重用的“点击编辑”指令</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://responsiblysourced.wordpress.com/2013/07/08/reactive-real-time-log-search-with-play-akka-angularjs-and-elasticsearch/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">基于Play、Akka、AngularJS和Elasticsearch的实时响应日志查询</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://www.firebase.com/blog/2013-07-16-build-your-own-feed-reader.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">还在想念Googler Reader？使用Firebase和AngularJS做自己的阅读器</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://abou-kone.com/2013/07/17/developing-a-mobile-app-with-phonegap-angularjs-and-expressjs-part-i/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使用Phonegap、AngularJS和ExpressJS创建一个移动应用（第一部分）</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://matthiasnehlsen.com/blog/2013/08/13/birdwatch-angularjs-elasticsearch-play/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">BirdWatch v0.2：基于AngularJS，ElasticSearch和Play框架的Tweet流分析</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.opensourceconnections.com/2013/08/25/instant-search-with-solr-and-angular/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">基于Solr和AngularJS的即时搜索</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/amirrajan/sortis" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Sorties：Twitter重度用户的客户端，也是程序员开发基于twitter程序的跳板</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://timothy.userapp.io/post/64117882900/customizable-twitter-timeline-for-angularjs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS打造的可定制的Twitter Timeline</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://seanhess.github.io/2013/10/14/angularjs-directive-design.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使AngularJS指令设计变得简单</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader2">AngularJS指令</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.phloxblog.in/jquery-plugin-angular-js-directive-clean-html-approach/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">为jQuery插件创建AngularJS指令</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.phloxblog.in/d3-js-angular-directive/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">为D3.js柱状图创建AngularJS指令</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.directiv.es/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">www.directiv.es：一个AngularJS指令资源库</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/agrublev/Angular-localStorage" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS 本地存储</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://twofuckingdevelopers.com/2013/08/videogular-an-html5-video-player-for-angularjs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Videogular：AngularJS打造的HTML5视频播放器</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://jmdobry.github.io/angular-cache/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS 缓存</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://angular-ui.github.io/bootstrap/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Twitter Bootstrap的AngularJS指令</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/wesleyhales/angular-charts" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Angular的图表指令(directive)和服务(service)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://modernjavascript.blogspot.com.au/2013/10/angularjs-table-sort.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">表格排序</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader3">AngularJS 游戏</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.sitepoint.com/angularjs-tutorial-build-an-app-using-directives-and-data-binding/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">CoffeeScript写的一个OX小游戏</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/callmehiphop/mario-cards" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">超级马里奥卡片翻转游戏</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader4">AngularJS开发流程和测试</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.youtube.com/watchv=UYVcY9EJcRs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS测试策略[Youtube视频]</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.portlandwebworks.com/blog/combining-yeoman-angularjs-and-cordova-mobile-development" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使用Yeoman，AngularJS和Cordova做移动应用开发</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.youtube.com/watchv=eUmDDxrvqSs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">用Angular和Yeoman开发Chrome应用简介[Youtube视频]</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.phloxblog.in/angular-js-tests-jasmine/#.UfzX3pI3CSp" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">用Jasmine测试AngularJS应用</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.yearofmoo.com/2013/01/full-spectrum-testing-with-angularjs-and-karma.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使用Karma对AngularJS应用做全方位的测试</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/m7r/grunt-ngdocs" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">使用一个Grunt task创建AngularJS文档</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/joshdmiller/ng-boilerplate" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">ng-boilerplate：一个AngularJS新项目的样板项目</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://github.com/angular/angularjs-batarang" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Chrome的AngularJS监控插件</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://weblogs.asp.net/dwahlin/archive/2013/08/30/using-the-angularjs-package-for-sublime-text.aspx" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">在Sublime Text中使用AngularJS包</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id="articleHeader5">AngularJS书籍（英文）</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="http://www.manning.com/bford/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS实战</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://leanpub.com/ng-book" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AngularJS入门指南</a></li>\r\n	<li><a style="color: #008e59;" href="https://www.packtpub.com/angularjs-web-application-development/book" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">精通AngularJS Web应用开发</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '2014年Angularjs学习资源精选', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-07 16:15:36', '2014-12-07 08:15:36', '', 8, 'http://ngionic.com/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(10, 1, '2014-12-08 22:20:16', '2014-12-08 14:20:16', 'AngularJs是Google开源的前端JS框架。使用AngularJs, 我们能够容易地、健壮的开发出类似于Gmail一样的单页Web应用。AngularJs这个新兴的MVC前端框架，具有以下特点: MVC, 模块化，自动化双向数据绑定，语义化标签、依赖注入等。\r\n<h2><strong>AngularJs和Jquery的有什么不同?</strong></h2>\r\nJquery的主要目的是简化Js编写，专注于浏览器跨平台，主要用来操作DOM.\r\nAngularJs主要关注Html数据的获取和呈现，以及应对日益复杂的Web应用需求，使得开发庞大的Web应用能够更加容易。\r\n<h2><strong>AngularJs呈现页面的原理</strong></h2>\r\nAnguarJs提供了一些对于Html进行加强的语义标签(directive)，这些标签在浏览器加载完页面后被执行。举例来说:\r\n<div class="sycode">\r\n<pre class="precsshui">&lt;table id=”leaderBoard”&gt;\r\n          &lt;thead&gt;\r\n              &lt;tr&gt;\r\n                  &lt;th&gt;Id&lt;/th&gt;\r\n                  &lt;th&gt;Name&lt;/th&gt;\r\n                  &lt;th&gt;Salary&lt;/th&gt;\r\n              &lt;/tr&gt;\r\n          &lt;/thead&gt;\r\n          &lt;tbody&gt;\r\n              &lt;tr ng-repeat="user in users"&gt;\r\n                  &lt;td&gt;{{user.Id}}&lt;/td&gt;\r\n                  &lt;td&gt;{{user.Name}}&lt;/td&gt;\r\n                  &lt;td&gt;{{user.Salary}}&lt;/td&gt;\r\n              &lt;/tr&gt;\r\n          &lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n上面的ng-repeat，就是一个directive, 相当于一个for循环。在页面加载完成后，AngularJs会遍历users数据对象，来呈现(render)出这个table中的内容。\r\n<h2><strong>如何实现在render完成之后，执行Js脚本</strong></h2>\r\n当我们使用Jquery结合AngulraJs使用的时候，希望在render完table后，执行一段js脚本，把JqTable应用到该table上。在实际开发中，会经常碰到这样的需求，希望能够捕获到AngularJs渲染完成页面的事件。\r\n要达到这个目的，我们需要为当前的app自定义directive:\r\n<div class="sycode">\r\n<pre class="precsshui">app.directive(''onFinishRenderFilters'', function ($timeout) {\r\n    return {\r\n        restrict: ''A'',\r\n        link: function(scope, element, attr) {\r\n            if (scope.$last === true) {\r\n                $timeout(function() {\r\n                    scope.$emit(''ngRepeatFinished'');\r\n                });\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    };\r\n});</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n然后，在我们需要监控的地方，加上该directive:\r\n<div class="sycode">\r\n<pre class="precsshui">&lt;tr ng-repeat="user in users" on-finish-render-filters&gt;\r\n      &lt;td&gt;{{user.Id}}&lt;/td&gt;\r\n      &lt;td&gt;{{user.Name}}&lt;/td&gt;\r\n      &lt;td&gt;{{user.Salary}}&lt;/td&gt;\r\n&lt;/tr&gt;</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n最后，补充上我们需要render完成之后的Js脚本:\r\n<div class="sycode">\r\n<pre class="precsshui">$scope.$on(''ngRepeatFinished'', function (ngRepeatFinishedEvent) {\r\n          //下面是在table render完成后执行的js\r\n          var table = $("#leaderBoard").dataTable({\r\n              bJQueryUI: true,\r\n              "sScrollX": ''100%'',\r\n          });\r\n});</pre>\r\n</div>', 'AngularJs中，如何在render完成之后，执行Js脚本', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'angularjs%e4%b8%ad%ef%bc%8c%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e5%9c%a8render%e5%ae%8c%e6%88%90%e4%b9%8b%e5%90%8e%ef%bc%8c%e6%89%a7%e8%a1%8cjs%e8%84%9a%e6%9c%ac', '', '', '2014-12-08 22:20:16', '2014-12-08 14:20:16', '', 0, 'http://ngionic.com/?p=10', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(12, 1, '2014-12-07 21:48:36', '2014-12-07 13:48:36', '<div class="entry-intro">\r\n<div class="entry-excerpt">这篇<a title="2014年Angularjs学习资源精选" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/" target="_blank"><em><strong>AngularJS</strong></em></a> 教程会让你通过一个精简指令集和补习，包你30分钟内全部用AngularJS 知识。在这短暂而详细的用AngularJS 教程你将能够快速创建功能强大的、直观的Web应用程序。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="entry-content">\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">开始 <a title="2014年Angularjs学习资源精选" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/" target="_blank"><em><strong>AngularJS</strong></em></a></h2>\r\n先做准备工作建一个 <strong>AngularJS</strong>的静态页面. 命名为index.html代码如下:\r\n<pre><code style="color: green;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n     &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在我们可以通打开 <a href="http://angularjs.org/" target="_blank">http://angularjs.org/</a> 并复制最新<strong>AngularJS </strong>库的CDN.或者下载一份最新的到本地将他引入到你的index.html的头部中:\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n     &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n     &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.2.8/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n     &lt;div id=''content''&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n好了，我们就有一个包含angularjs的基础的静态页面了，继续往下.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">用Angularjs也配置你的页面</h2>\r\n我们要告诉Angularjs将我们页面渲染成一个应用. 我们这个<strong>AngularJS 教程</strong>不会涉及到多应用和多Controller的页面,我们只是做一个单页面应用\r\n\r\n在容器外加上 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-app=”MyTutorialApp”</span> :\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp''&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在我们告诉 <strong>AngularJS</strong> 这个div是一个应用，并声明他对应的controller是谁:\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span> 只是我起的一个controller名称, controllers的生声明应该语义化些.一些人认为，这仍然定义的不够，这是个简单的教程！好的，现在我们知道在#content div都将由主<span style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span>控制的，但他是在哪里？我们需要做的！在同一个目录作为您的index.html文件，我们需要创建一个js文件称为app.js和它看起来应该像下面：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\nvar app = angular.module(''MyTutorialApp'',[]);\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n所有这些文件将建立一个 名为<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MyTutorialApp</span><span class="inline-code" style="color: #666666;">的</span><strong>AngularJS</strong> app 并给它分配到应用程序变量，我们可以以后用。现在我们需要创建另一个文件中称，maincontroller.js应如下：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n		\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n这是分配一个控制器，控制器的<span style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MyTutorialApp</span>应用。这一切的JavaScript可以放在相同的JavaScript文件，但它是很好的做法，将它们以保持你的代码的可维护性和容易理解。记住，app.js需要在maincontroller.js之前包含进来。让我们现在这样做，包括HTML文件内，我们就可以开始了！\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在我们就搭好一个简单的<strong>Angularjs</strong>的应用了，继续：\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">理解$scope</h2>\r\n当我们创造了maincontroller.js代码，你可能已经注意到，我们增加了$scope变量作为参数的控制器的功能。这是我们将我们所有的控制器的变量，然后将使他们可以在HTML页面的#content div。看看下面的例子来理解这个概念。声明一个变量控制器$scope：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n    $scope.understand = "I now understand how the scope works!";\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n在上述代码中，我们简单地创建了一个$scope分配一个字符串到它。现在我们可以在我们的<span class="high-light-bg">HTML</span>。\r\n<pre class="prettyprint"><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n			{{understand}}\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n在上述HTML我们将了解变量{ {} }所以用AngularJS知道它需要做些什么。注意我们没有增加了范围。对变量名称前面。如果您现在查看您的index.html文件在一个浏览器，你应该看到如下\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-670" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/understandscope.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Scope" width="578" height="274" /></div>\r\n现在你应该明白什么是变量的范围是，他们也可以在HTML，然后用包装带{ }。你也应该明白，这仅仅是可用的域控制器，那么你不可能访问的变量，从 “knowledge” 的变量超出了#content div，除非该控制器是确定的。\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">理解绑定</h2>\r\n所以，那很酷，我们可以声明一个变量的范围内JS和即时访问它在HTML，但用AngularJS可以提供这么多。数据绑定是一个很大的主题，但这用AngularJS教程将涵盖了最重要的部分，以确保你明白什么是可能的，允许你进一步调查你自己（或等待更多的用AngularJS教程：D）。要理解这一概念，可以声明一个scope变量将作为一个模型。修改maincontroller.js看起来如下：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n     $scope.inputValue = "";\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在，让我们添加一些额外的HTML页：\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n		&lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''inputValue'' /&gt;\r\n		{{inputValue}}\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n上面我们添加了简单的文本输入框并用 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-model</span>绑定到scope变量 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">inputValue</span>. 注意我们并没有用 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">{{}}</span> 包含它就像我们前面的 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-*</span> 标签. 另外我们将 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">inputValue</span> scope 变量加入到页面像前面的<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">understand</span> 变量一样.\r\n\r\n这样我们有界输入值的变量。这意味着每当输入值的变化，变量将更新以符合本。在Web浏览器中打开网页，并开始输入在输入框。你应该看到类似下面的：\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-671" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/binding1.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Binding" width="492" height="198" /></div>\r\n当我们输入新值时scope变量也更新了，和你输入的值同步, 有意思吧! 现在你有办法维持各种元素和价值的同步页面内。让我们转移到一个更复杂的例子来更好地了解什么是可能的。更新maincontroller.js看起来像下面<span class="high-light-bg">：</span>\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n	$scope.selectedPerson = 0;\r\n	$scope.selectedGenre = null;\r\n	$scope.people = [\r\n		{\r\n			id: 0,\r\n			name: ''Leon'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Rock'',\r\n				''Metal'',\r\n				''Dubstep'',\r\n				''Electro''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 1,\r\n			name: ''Chris'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Indie'',\r\n				''Drumstep'',\r\n				''Dubstep'',\r\n				''Electro''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 2,\r\n			name: ''Harry'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Rock'',\r\n				''Metal'',\r\n				''Thrash Metal'',\r\n				''Heavy Metal''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 3,\r\n			name: ''Allyce'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Pop'',\r\n				''RnB'',\r\n				''Hip Hop''\r\n			]\r\n		}\r\n	];\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span class="high-light-bg">我们已经声明了三个scope变量，selectedPerson 要选择的人的对象。</span>selectedGenre要举行的选定类型的字符串值。最后我们有一个数组对象包含他们自己的音乐品味。我们希望达到的是有两个选择下拉。你将能够选择的人，那么其他的，由于结合会自动更新，允许你选择的人的音乐。让我们添加这个HTML元素到我们的网页：\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n		&lt;select ng-model=''selectedPerson'' ng-options=''obj.name for obj in people''&gt;&lt;/select&gt;\r\n		&lt;select ng-model=''selectedGenre''&gt;\r\n			&lt;option ng-repeat=''label in people[selectedPerson.id].music''&gt;{{label}}&lt;/option&gt;\r\n		&lt;/select&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n有一些新的位在这里让我们看看他们了。首先我们有一个选择与NG选项标签输入。这使我们能够从人的scope变量的值填充该选择输入，使用的名称属性的人的对象内的标签，选择选项的实际价值，对象本身。本文用AngularJS教程是不会去考虑的NG选项，你可以阅读更多关于这伟大的细节。玩耍，看到什么是可能的。\r\n\r\n下一个选择输入填充本身是一种不同的方式，为示范的目的。“NG的重复”在我心中是一个用AngularJS的最强大的功能。NG的重复简单的允许你复制基于数组或对象集合的HTML元素。在上述“NG的重复”将在基于selectedpersons ID值是由选定的第一个框确定我们已经宣布selectedperson为模型，我们以前的输入people.music阵列创建的每一个音乐流派的HTML的一个选项。\r\n<p class="alert-info"><strong>注意:</strong> <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat </span>可以用在所有的html标签上!</p>\r\nNG连续选择标签我们将{ {label} }在打开和关闭的选项标签，这是输出的标签，我们宣布在NG的重复。在浏览器中打开它，选择一个人，你应该看到类似下面的：\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-672" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/binding2.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Binding" width="492" height="229" /></div>\r\n所以你可以看到，我们已经使用了模型绑定的选择值，那么我们就可以用这个地方相同的范围内是可更新的<span class="high-light-bg">其他元素</span>！\r\n<p class="alert-info"><strong>注意:</strong> people[selectedPerson.id].music 只作为 people ID#s作为数组索引相同的。这会不会是一个真实的世界形势的一个理想的解决方案，因为你不能保证人的身份#将匹配的<span class="high-light-bg">数组索引</span>。</p>\r\nYou should now have a good understanding of what binding is about and what is possible. We have also looked at ng-repeat and ng-options two powerful features of <strong>AngularJS</strong>.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">ANGULARJS数据过滤</h2>\r\n<span class="high-light-bg">本文用AngularJS教程是现在要盖过滤，因为这是另一个超级强大的用AngularJS特征。</span>我们要利用人范围阵列从前面的部分，创建一个简单的界面，将允许我们寻找的人的名字和结果输出到一个页面。为更新您的HTML：\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n在这里，我们增加了一个文本输入提供了一个模型<span style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">searchText</span>我们不需要声明这个身体范围内maincontroller.js。我们还创建了一个联合国的命令列表，添加一个NG的重复的元素列表，这将创建一个在我们在上一节中创建的阵列中每个人的列表元素的人。如果你打开这个在你的浏览器，你可以看到下面的：\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-673" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/filter1.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Filtering" width="575" height="232" /></div>\r\n你可以看到在人们阵列显示在列表的搜索输入下的所有人的名字。回顾在HTML中我们可以看到在NG的重复一些额外的代码。我们已经添加了一个管|然后指定的筛选并对模型。这将调用用AngularJS滤波器指令和它提供所要查找的文字模式。NG的重复将显示基于过滤器的返回结果。走在前面，在文本框中输入的东西，看到的结果自动更新。\r\n\r\n过滤器就这么简单! 这个<strong>AngularJS</strong> 教程不会介绍到更高级的过滤器或自定义过滤器,但是后面会有更多<a title="Angularjs教程" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/"><strong>AngularJS 教程</strong></a>!\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">ANGULARJS显示隐藏</h2>\r\n<strong>AngularJS </strong>这部分教程<span class="high-light-bg">要看你如何隐藏和显示元件。</span>我们要继续使用人阵列作为我们的数据集但我们需要添加一些额外的数据允许我们表明ng-show和ng-hide。更新你的maincontroller.js文件如下：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n  $scope.people = [\r\n        {\r\n            id: 0,\r\n            name: ''Leon'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 1,\r\n            name: ''Chris'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Indie'',\r\n                ''Drumstep'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 2,\r\n            name: ''Harry'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Thrash Metal'',\r\n                ''Heavy Metal''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: false\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 3,\r\n            name: ''Allyce'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Pop'',\r\n                ''RnB'',\r\n                ''Hip Hop''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        }\r\n    ];\r\n});\r\n</code></pre>\r\n你可以看到，我们已经添加了一个动态的标签，每个人，与设置为false，国旗的唯一的人是哈利。表明ng-hide和ng-show，添加一个额外的联合的命令你的HTML列表如下：\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n这将简单将数据输出两次。现在我们将开始使用<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> 和<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> 基于我们创建的活动标签的值. 更新你的HTML如下:\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-show=''person.live == true''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-hide=''person.live == false''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n正如我们所见 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> 和 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> 使用完全相同的方式, <span class="high-light-bg">除非他们是彼此相反的（明显的）。</span>在上面的例子中，我们引用的个人变量声明为NG的重复和公正的评价是否活的属性是真还是假部分。如果你打开这个例子在您的浏览器中你会看到哈利不再出现在任一列表。\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/filter2.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Filtering" width="575" height="331" /></div>\r\n用AngularJS隐藏或显示一个元素是多么容易地\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">ANGULARJS事件</h2>\r\n这种快速的用AngularJS教程的最后一部分将在事件。<span class="high-light-bg">事件一直JavaScript框架如jQuery，这并没有改变用AngularJS一个强大的功能。</span>说明我们要添加另一个输入和一个按钮，我们的HTML如下：\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-show=''person.live == true''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''newPerson'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;button ng-click=''addNew()''&gt;Add&lt;/button&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n我们只是添加了一个 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">newPerson</span> 的输入框和一个按钮用ng-click绑定了addNew的响应函数. <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span>文件更新如下:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n  $scope.people = [\r\n        {\r\n            id: 0,\r\n            name: ''Leon'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 1,\r\n            name: ''Chris'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Indie'',\r\n                ''Drumstep'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 2,\r\n            name: ''Harry'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Thrash Metal'',\r\n                ''Heavy Metal''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: false\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 3,\r\n            name: ''Allyce'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Pop'',\r\n                ''RnB'',\r\n                ''Hip Hop''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        }\r\n    ];\r\n    $scope.newPerson = null;\r\n    $scope.addNew = function() {\r\n        if ($scope.newPerson != null &amp;&amp; $scope.newPerson != "") {\r\n            $scope.people.push({\r\n                id: $scope.people.length,\r\n                name: $scope.newPerson,\r\n                live: true,\r\n                music: []\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n});\r\n</code></pre>\r\n上述JS表明我们已经宣布新的$scope变量和一个$scope的方法AddNew的按钮。\r\n\r\n在新的功能，我们只是检查，新的值不为空或空，然后添加一个新的对象的数组的末尾的人。这是一个很简单的例子，如何可以用在用AngularJS单击事件。有许多可用的如NG变化，NG检查，NG的选择，但这不会用AngularJS教程等进入更多的细节，你可以在用AngularJS如果你想了解更多。\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">总结</h2>\r\n这种快速的用AngularJS教程应该给你足够的了解如何用AngularJS作品在一个很高的水平，它是能够。你现在应该能够继续开始创建您自己的用AngularJS应用学习更多。\r\n\r\n在学习的同时，我发现文档不是很大，它采取了很多的实验和找工作的例子用AngularJS。我希望本教程让你起来，用AngularJS约30分钟的运行。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n备注：简单百度翻译了一下\r\n\r\n</div>', '30分钟带你了解angularjs', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '30-minutes-learn-angular', '', '', '2014-12-09 20:47:48', '2014-12-09 12:47:48', '', 0, 'http://ngionic.com/?page_id=12', 0, 'page', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(34, 1, '2014-12-09 20:47:48', '2014-12-09 12:47:48', '<div class="entry-intro">\r\n<div class="entry-excerpt">这篇<a title="2014年Angularjs学习资源精选" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/" target="_blank"><em><strong>AngularJS</strong></em></a> 教程会让你通过一个精简指令集和补习，包你30分钟内全部用AngularJS 知识。在这短暂而详细的用AngularJS 教程你将能够快速创建功能强大的、直观的Web应用程序。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="entry-content">\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">开始 <a title="2014年Angularjs学习资源精选" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/" target="_blank"><em><strong>AngularJS</strong></em></a></h2>\r\n先做准备工作建一个 <strong>AngularJS</strong>的静态页面. 命名为index.html代码如下:\r\n<pre><code style="color: green;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n     &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在我们可以通打开 <a href="http://angularjs.org/" target="_blank">http://angularjs.org/</a> 并复制最新<strong>AngularJS </strong>库的CDN.或者下载一份最新的到本地将他引入到你的index.html的头部中:\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n     &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n     &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.2.8/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n     &lt;div id=''content''&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n好了，我们就有一个包含angularjs的基础的静态页面了，继续往下.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">用Angularjs也配置你的页面</h2>\r\n我们要告诉Angularjs将我们页面渲染成一个应用. 我们这个<strong>AngularJS 教程</strong>不会涉及到多应用和多Controller的页面,我们只是做一个单页面应用\r\n\r\n在容器外加上 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-app=”MyTutorialApp”</span> :\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp''&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在我们告诉 <strong>AngularJS</strong> 这个div是一个应用，并声明他对应的controller是谁:\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span> 只是我起的一个controller名称, controllers的生声明应该语义化些.一些人认为，这仍然定义的不够，这是个简单的教程！好的，现在我们知道在#content div都将由主<span style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span>控制的，但他是在哪里？我们需要做的！在同一个目录作为您的index.html文件，我们需要创建一个js文件称为app.js和它看起来应该像下面：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\nvar app = angular.module(''MyTutorialApp'',[]);\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n所有这些文件将建立一个 名为<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MyTutorialApp</span><span class="inline-code" style="color: #666666;">的</span><strong>AngularJS</strong> app 并给它分配到应用程序变量，我们可以以后用。现在我们需要创建另一个文件中称，maincontroller.js应如下：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n		\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n这是分配一个控制器，控制器的<span style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MyTutorialApp</span>应用。这一切的JavaScript可以放在相同的JavaScript文件，但它是很好的做法，将它们以保持你的代码的可维护性和容易理解。记住，app.js需要在maincontroller.js之前包含进来。让我们现在这样做，包括HTML文件内，我们就可以开始了！\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在我们就搭好一个简单的<strong>Angularjs</strong>的应用了，继续：\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">理解$scope</h2>\r\n当我们创造了maincontroller.js代码，你可能已经注意到，我们增加了$scope变量作为参数的控制器的功能。这是我们将我们所有的控制器的变量，然后将使他们可以在HTML页面的#content div。看看下面的例子来理解这个概念。声明一个变量控制器$scope：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n    $scope.understand = "I now understand how the scope works!";\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n在上述代码中，我们简单地创建了一个$scope分配一个字符串到它。现在我们可以在我们的<span class="high-light-bg">HTML</span>。\r\n<pre class="prettyprint"><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n			{{understand}}\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n在上述HTML我们将了解变量{ {} }所以用AngularJS知道它需要做些什么。注意我们没有增加了范围。对变量名称前面。如果您现在查看您的index.html文件在一个浏览器，你应该看到如下\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-670" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/understandscope.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Scope" width="578" height="274" /></div>\r\n现在你应该明白什么是变量的范围是，他们也可以在HTML，然后用包装带{ }。你也应该明白，这仅仅是可用的域控制器，那么你不可能访问的变量，从 “knowledge” 的变量超出了#content div，除非该控制器是确定的。\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">理解绑定</h2>\r\n所以，那很酷，我们可以声明一个变量的范围内JS和即时访问它在HTML，但用AngularJS可以提供这么多。数据绑定是一个很大的主题，但这用AngularJS教程将涵盖了最重要的部分，以确保你明白什么是可能的，允许你进一步调查你自己（或等待更多的用AngularJS教程：D）。要理解这一概念，可以声明一个scope变量将作为一个模型。修改maincontroller.js看起来如下：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n     $scope.inputValue = "";\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在，让我们添加一些额外的HTML页：\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n		&lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''inputValue'' /&gt;\r\n		{{inputValue}}\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n上面我们添加了简单的文本输入框并用 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-model</span>绑定到scope变量 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">inputValue</span>. 注意我们并没有用 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">{{}}</span> 包含它就像我们前面的 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-*</span> 标签. 另外我们将 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">inputValue</span> scope 变量加入到页面像前面的<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">understand</span> 变量一样.\r\n\r\n这样我们有界输入值的变量。这意味着每当输入值的变化，变量将更新以符合本。在Web浏览器中打开网页，并开始输入在输入框。你应该看到类似下面的：\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-671" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/binding1.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Binding" width="492" height="198" /></div>\r\n当我们输入新值时scope变量也更新了，和你输入的值同步, 有意思吧! 现在你有办法维持各种元素和价值的同步页面内。让我们转移到一个更复杂的例子来更好地了解什么是可能的。更新maincontroller.js看起来像下面<span class="high-light-bg">：</span>\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n	$scope.selectedPerson = 0;\r\n	$scope.selectedGenre = null;\r\n	$scope.people = [\r\n		{\r\n			id: 0,\r\n			name: ''Leon'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Rock'',\r\n				''Metal'',\r\n				''Dubstep'',\r\n				''Electro''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 1,\r\n			name: ''Chris'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Indie'',\r\n				''Drumstep'',\r\n				''Dubstep'',\r\n				''Electro''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 2,\r\n			name: ''Harry'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Rock'',\r\n				''Metal'',\r\n				''Thrash Metal'',\r\n				''Heavy Metal''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 3,\r\n			name: ''Allyce'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Pop'',\r\n				''RnB'',\r\n				''Hip Hop''\r\n			]\r\n		}\r\n	];\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span class="high-light-bg">我们已经声明了三个scope变量，selectedPerson 要选择的人的对象。</span>selectedGenre要举行的选定类型的字符串值。最后我们有一个数组对象包含他们自己的音乐品味。我们希望达到的是有两个选择下拉。你将能够选择的人，那么其他的，由于结合会自动更新，允许你选择的人的音乐。让我们添加这个HTML元素到我们的网页：\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n		&lt;select ng-model=''selectedPerson'' ng-options=''obj.name for obj in people''&gt;&lt;/select&gt;\r\n		&lt;select ng-model=''selectedGenre''&gt;\r\n			&lt;option ng-repeat=''label in people[selectedPerson.id].music''&gt;{{label}}&lt;/option&gt;\r\n		&lt;/select&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n有一些新的位在这里让我们看看他们了。首先我们有一个选择与NG选项标签输入。这使我们能够从人的scope变量的值填充该选择输入，使用的名称属性的人的对象内的标签，选择选项的实际价值，对象本身。本文用AngularJS教程是不会去考虑的NG选项，你可以阅读更多关于这伟大的细节。玩耍，看到什么是可能的。\r\n\r\n下一个选择输入填充本身是一种不同的方式，为示范的目的。“NG的重复”在我心中是一个用AngularJS的最强大的功能。NG的重复简单的允许你复制基于数组或对象集合的HTML元素。在上述“NG的重复”将在基于selectedpersons ID值是由选定的第一个框确定我们已经宣布selectedperson为模型，我们以前的输入people.music阵列创建的每一个音乐流派的HTML的一个选项。\r\n<p class="alert-info"><strong>注意:</strong> <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat </span>可以用在所有的html标签上!</p>\r\nNG连续选择标签我们将{ {label} }在打开和关闭的选项标签，这是输出的标签，我们宣布在NG的重复。在浏览器中打开它，选择一个人，你应该看到类似下面的：\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-672" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/binding2.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Binding" width="492" height="229" /></div>\r\n所以你可以看到，我们已经使用了模型绑定的选择值，那么我们就可以用这个地方相同的范围内是可更新的<span class="high-light-bg">其他元素</span>！\r\n<p class="alert-info"><strong>注意:</strong> people[selectedPerson.id].music 只作为 people ID#s作为数组索引相同的。这会不会是一个真实的世界形势的一个理想的解决方案，因为你不能保证人的身份#将匹配的<span class="high-light-bg">数组索引</span>。</p>\r\nYou should now have a good understanding of what binding is about and what is possible. We have also looked at ng-repeat and ng-options two powerful features of <strong>AngularJS</strong>.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">ANGULARJS数据过滤</h2>\r\n<span class="high-light-bg">本文用AngularJS教程是现在要盖过滤，因为这是另一个超级强大的用AngularJS特征。</span>我们要利用人范围阵列从前面的部分，创建一个简单的界面，将允许我们寻找的人的名字和结果输出到一个页面。为更新您的HTML：\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n在这里，我们增加了一个文本输入提供了一个模型<span style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">searchText</span>我们不需要声明这个身体范围内maincontroller.js。我们还创建了一个联合国的命令列表，添加一个NG的重复的元素列表，这将创建一个在我们在上一节中创建的阵列中每个人的列表元素的人。如果你打开这个在你的浏览器，你可以看到下面的：\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-673" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/filter1.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Filtering" width="575" height="232" /></div>\r\n你可以看到在人们阵列显示在列表的搜索输入下的所有人的名字。回顾在HTML中我们可以看到在NG的重复一些额外的代码。我们已经添加了一个管|然后指定的筛选并对模型。这将调用用AngularJS滤波器指令和它提供所要查找的文字模式。NG的重复将显示基于过滤器的返回结果。走在前面，在文本框中输入的东西，看到的结果自动更新。\r\n\r\n过滤器就这么简单! 这个<strong>AngularJS</strong> 教程不会介绍到更高级的过滤器或自定义过滤器,但是后面会有更多<a title="Angularjs教程" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/"><strong>AngularJS 教程</strong></a>!\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">ANGULARJS显示隐藏</h2>\r\n<strong>AngularJS </strong>这部分教程<span class="high-light-bg">要看你如何隐藏和显示元件。</span>我们要继续使用人阵列作为我们的数据集但我们需要添加一些额外的数据允许我们表明ng-show和ng-hide。更新你的maincontroller.js文件如下：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n  $scope.people = [\r\n        {\r\n            id: 0,\r\n            name: ''Leon'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 1,\r\n            name: ''Chris'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Indie'',\r\n                ''Drumstep'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 2,\r\n            name: ''Harry'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Thrash Metal'',\r\n                ''Heavy Metal''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: false\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 3,\r\n            name: ''Allyce'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Pop'',\r\n                ''RnB'',\r\n                ''Hip Hop''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        }\r\n    ];\r\n});\r\n</code></pre>\r\n你可以看到，我们已经添加了一个动态的标签，每个人，与设置为false，国旗的唯一的人是哈利。表明ng-hide和ng-show，添加一个额外的联合的命令你的HTML列表如下：\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n这将简单将数据输出两次。现在我们将开始使用<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> 和<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> 基于我们创建的活动标签的值. 更新你的HTML如下:\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-show=''person.live == true''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-hide=''person.live == false''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n正如我们所见 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> 和 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> 使用完全相同的方式, <span class="high-light-bg">除非他们是彼此相反的（明显的）。</span>在上面的例子中，我们引用的个人变量声明为NG的重复和公正的评价是否活的属性是真还是假部分。如果你打开这个例子在您的浏览器中你会看到哈利不再出现在任一列表。\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/filter2.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Filtering" width="575" height="331" /></div>\r\n用AngularJS隐藏或显示一个元素是多么容易地\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">ANGULARJS事件</h2>\r\n这种快速的用AngularJS教程的最后一部分将在事件。<span class="high-light-bg">事件一直JavaScript框架如jQuery，这并没有改变用AngularJS一个强大的功能。</span>说明我们要添加另一个输入和一个按钮，我们的HTML如下：\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-show=''person.live == true''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''newPerson'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;button ng-click=''addNew()''&gt;Add&lt;/button&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n我们只是添加了一个 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">newPerson</span> 的输入框和一个按钮用ng-click绑定了addNew的响应函数. <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span>文件更新如下:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n  $scope.people = [\r\n        {\r\n            id: 0,\r\n            name: ''Leon'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 1,\r\n            name: ''Chris'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Indie'',\r\n                ''Drumstep'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 2,\r\n            name: ''Harry'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Thrash Metal'',\r\n                ''Heavy Metal''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: false\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 3,\r\n            name: ''Allyce'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Pop'',\r\n                ''RnB'',\r\n                ''Hip Hop''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        }\r\n    ];\r\n    $scope.newPerson = null;\r\n    $scope.addNew = function() {\r\n        if ($scope.newPerson != null &amp;&amp; $scope.newPerson != "") {\r\n            $scope.people.push({\r\n                id: $scope.people.length,\r\n                name: $scope.newPerson,\r\n                live: true,\r\n                music: []\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n});\r\n</code></pre>\r\n上述JS表明我们已经宣布新的$scope变量和一个$scope的方法AddNew的按钮。\r\n\r\n在新的功能，我们只是检查，新的值不为空或空，然后添加一个新的对象的数组的末尾的人。这是一个很简单的例子，如何可以用在用AngularJS单击事件。有许多可用的如NG变化，NG检查，NG的选择，但这不会用AngularJS教程等进入更多的细节，你可以在用AngularJS如果你想了解更多。\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">总结</h2>\r\n这种快速的用AngularJS教程应该给你足够的了解如何用AngularJS作品在一个很高的水平，它是能够。你现在应该能够继续开始创建您自己的用AngularJS应用学习更多。\r\n\r\n在学习的同时，我发现文档不是很大，它采取了很多的实验和找工作的例子用AngularJS。我希望本教程让你起来，用AngularJS约30分钟的运行。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n备注：简单百度翻译了一下\r\n\r\n</div>', '30分钟带你了解angularjs', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-09 20:47:48', '2014-12-09 12:47:48', '', 12, 'http://ngionic.com/2014/12/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(16, 1, '2014-12-07 23:17:22', '2014-12-07 15:17:22', '<div class="entry-intro">\r\n<div class="entry-excerpt">这篇<a title="2014年Angularjs学习资源精选" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/" target="_blank"><em><strong>AngularJS</strong></em></a> 教程会让你通过一个精简指令集和补习，包你30分钟内全部用AngularJS 知识。在这短暂而详细的用AngularJS 教程你将能够快速创建功能强大的、直观的Web应用程序。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="entry-content">\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">开始 <a title="2014年Angularjs学习资源精选" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/" target="_blank"><em><strong>AngularJS</strong></em></a></h2>\r\n先做准备工作建一个 <strong>AngularJS</strong>的静态页面. 命名为index.html代码如下:\r\n<pre><code style="color: green;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n     &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在我们可以通打开 <a href="http://angularjs.org/" target="_blank">http://angularjs.org/</a> 并复制最新<strong>AngularJS </strong>库的CDN.或者下载一份最新的到本地将他引入到你的index.html的头部中:\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n     &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n     &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.2.8/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n     &lt;div id=''content''&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n好了，我们就有一个包含angularjs的基础的静态页面了，继续往下.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">用Angularjs也配置你的页面</h2>\r\n我们要告诉Angularjs将我们页面渲染成一个应用. 我们这个<strong>AngularJS 教程</strong>不会涉及到多应用和多Controller的页面,我们只是做一个单页面应用\r\n\r\n在容器外加上 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-app=”MyTutorialApp”</span> :\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp''&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在我们告诉 <strong>AngularJS</strong> 这个div是一个应用，并声明他对应的controller是谁:\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span> 只是我起的一个controller名称, controllers的生声明应该语义化些.<span>一些人认为，这仍然定义的不够，这是个简单的教程！</span><span>好的，现在我们知道在#content div都将由主<span style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span>控制的，但他是在哪里？</span>我们需要做的！在同一个目录作为您的index.html文件，我们需要创建一个js文件称为<span>app.js</span>和<span>它看起来应该像</span><span>下面</span>：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\nvar app = angular.module(''MyTutorialApp'',[]);\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n所有这些文件将建立一个 名为<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MyTutorialApp</span><span class="inline-code" style="color: #666666;">的</span><strong>AngularJS</strong> app 并<span>给它分配到应用程序变量，我们可以以后用。</span>现在我们需要创建另一个文件中称，maincontroller.js应<span>如下</span><span>：</span>\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n		\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span>这是分配一个控制器，控制器的<span style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MyTutorialApp</span>应用。</span><span>这一切的JavaScript可以放在相同的JavaScript文件，但它是很好的做法，将它们以保持你的代码的可维护性和容易理解。</span>记住，app.js需要在maincontroller.js之前包含进来。让我们现在这样做，包括HTML文件内，<span>我们就可以开始了</span><span>！</span>\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在我们就搭好一个简单的<strong>Angularjs</strong>的应用了，继续：\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">理解$scope</h2>\r\n<span>当我们创造了maincontroller.js代码，你可能已经注意到，我们增加了$scope变量作为参数的控制器的功能。</span><span>这是我们将我们所有的控制器的变量，然后将使他们可以在HTML页面的#content div。</span><span>看看下面的例子来理解这个概念。</span>声明一个变量控制器$scope：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n    $scope.understand = "I now understand how the scope works!";\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span>在上述代码中，我们简单地创建了一个$scope分配一个字符串到它。</span>现在我们可以在我们的<span class="high-light-bg">HTML</span>。\r\n<pre class="prettyprint"><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n			{{understand}}\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span>在上述HTML我们将了解变量{ {} }所以用AngularJS知道它需要做些什么。</span>注意我们没有增加了范围。对变量名称前面。如果您现在查看您的index.html文件<span>在一个</span><span>浏览器</span>，<span>你</span><span>应该看到如下</span>\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-670" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/understandscope.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Scope" width="578" height="274" /></div>\r\n<span>现在你应该明白什么是变量的范围是，他们也可以在HTML，然后用包装带{ }。</span>你也应该明白，这<span>仅仅</span><span>是可用的</span>域控制器，那么你<span>不可能</span><span>访问的</span>变量，从 “knowledge” 的变量超出了#content div，除非该控制器是确定的<span>。</span>\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">理解绑定</h2>\r\n<span>所以，那很酷，我们可以声明一个变量的范围内JS和即时访问它在HTML，但用AngularJS可以提供这么多。</span><span>数据绑定是一个很大的主题，但这用AngularJS教程将涵盖了最重要的部分，以确保你明白什么是可能的，允许你进一步调查你自己（或等待更多的用AngularJS教程：D）。</span><span>要理解这一概念，可以声明一个scope变量将作为一个模型。</span>修改<span>maincontroller.js</span><span>看起来</span><span>如下</span><span>：</span>\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n     $scope.inputValue = "";\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在，让我们添加一些额外的HTML页<span>：</span>\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n		&lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''inputValue'' /&gt;\r\n		{{inputValue}}\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n上面我们添加了简单的文本输入框并用 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-model</span>绑定到scope变量 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">inputValue</span>. 注意我们并没有用 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">{{}}</span> 包含它就像我们前面的 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-*</span> 标签. 另外我们将 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">inputValue</span> scope 变量加入到页面像前面的<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">understand</span> 变量一样.\r\n\r\n<span>这样我们有界输入值的变量。</span>这意味着每当输入值的变化，变量将更新以符合本。在Web浏览器中打开网页，并开始输入在输入框。你应该看到类似下面的<span>：</span>\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-671" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/binding1.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Binding" width="492" height="198" /></div>\r\n当我们输入新值时scope变量也更新了，和你输入的值同步, 有意思吧! 现在你有办法维持各种元素和价值的同步页面内。<span>让我们转移到一个更复杂的例子来更好地了解什么是可能的。</span>更新maincontroller.js<span>看起来像下面</span><span class="high-light-bg">：</span>\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n	$scope.selectedPerson = 0;\r\n	$scope.selectedGenre = null;\r\n	$scope.people = [\r\n		{\r\n			id: 0,\r\n			name: ''Leon'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Rock'',\r\n				''Metal'',\r\n				''Dubstep'',\r\n				''Electro''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 1,\r\n			name: ''Chris'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Indie'',\r\n				''Drumstep'',\r\n				''Dubstep'',\r\n				''Electro''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 2,\r\n			name: ''Harry'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Rock'',\r\n				''Metal'',\r\n				''Thrash Metal'',\r\n				''Heavy Metal''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 3,\r\n			name: ''Allyce'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Pop'',\r\n				''RnB'',\r\n				''Hip Hop''\r\n			]\r\n		}\r\n	];\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span class="high-light-bg">我们已经声明了三个scope变量，selectedPerson 要选择的人的对象。</span><span>selectedGenre要举行的选定类型的字符串值。</span>最后我们有一个数组对象包含他们自己的音乐品味。我们希望达到的是有两个选择下拉。<span>你将能够选择的人，那么其他的，由于结合会自动更新，允许你选择的人的音乐。</span>让我们添加这个HTML元素到我们的网页：\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n		&lt;select ng-model=''selectedPerson'' ng-options=''obj.name for obj in people''&gt;&lt;/select&gt;\r\n		&lt;select ng-model=''selectedGenre''&gt;\r\n			&lt;option ng-repeat=''label in people[selectedPerson.id].music''&gt;{{label}}&lt;/option&gt;\r\n		&lt;/select&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span>有一些新的位在这里让我们看看他们了。</span>首先我们有一个选择与NG选项标签输入。<span>这使我们能够从人的scope变量的值填充该选择输入，使用的名称属性的人的对象内的标签，选择选项的实际价值，对象本身。</span><span>本文用AngularJS教程是不会去考虑的NG选项，你可以阅读更多关于这伟大的细节。</span>玩耍，看到<span>什么是可能的</span><span>。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>下一个选择输入填充本身是一种不同的方式，为示范的目的。</span><span>“NG的重复”在我心中是一个用AngularJS的最强大的功能。</span><span>NG的重复简单的允许你复制基于数组或对象集合的HTML元素。</span>在上述“NG的重复”将在基于selectedpersons ID值是由<span>选定的第一个</span>框<span>确定</span>我们已经宣布selectedperson<span>为</span><span>模型，</span>我们以前的输入people.music阵列<span>创建</span><span>的每一个</span><span>音乐流派</span><span>的</span>HTML<span>的一个选项</span><span>。</span>\r\n<p class="alert-info"><strong>注意:</strong> <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat </span>可以用在所有的html标签上!</p>\r\n<span>NG连续选择标签我们将{ {label} }在打开和关闭的选项标签，这是输出的标签，我们宣布在NG的重复。</span>在浏览器中打开它，选择一个人，你<span>应该看到类似</span><span>下面的</span><span>：</span>\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-672" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/binding2.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Binding" width="492" height="229" /></div>\r\n<span>所以你</span><span>可以看到，</span>我们已经使用了模型绑定的选择值，那么我们就可以用这个地方相同的范围内是可更新的<span class="high-light-bg">其他元素</span><span>！</span>\r\n<p class="alert-info"><strong>注意:</strong> people[selectedPerson.id].music 只作为 people ID#s<span>作为数组索引相同的。</span>这会不会是一个真实的世界形势的<span>一个理想的解决方案，</span>因为你不能保证人的身份#<span>将匹配的</span><span class="high-light-bg">数组索引</span><span>。</span></p>\r\nYou should now have a good understanding of what binding is about and what is possible. We have also looked at ng-repeat and ng-options two powerful features of <strong>AngularJS</strong>.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">ANGULARJS数据过滤</h2>\r\n<span class="high-light-bg">本文用AngularJS教程是现在要盖过滤，因为这是另一个超级强大的用AngularJS特征。</span><span>我们要利用人范围阵列从前面的部分，创建一个简单的界面，将允许我们寻找的人的名字和结果输出到一个页面。</span>为更新您的<span>HTML</span><span>：</span>\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span>在这里，我们增加了一个文本输入提供了一个模型<span style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">searchText</span>我们不需要声明这个身体范围内maincontroller.js。</span><span>我们还创建了一个联合国的命令列表，添加一个NG的重复的元素列表，这将创建一个在我们在上一节中创建的阵列中每个人的列表元素的人。</span>如果你打开这个在你的浏览器，你可以看到下面的<span>：</span>\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-673" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/filter1.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Filtering" width="575" height="232" /></div>\r\n你可以看到在人们阵列显示在列表的搜索输入下的所有人的名字。<span>回顾在HTML中我们可以看到在NG的重复一些额外的代码。</span>我们已经添加了一个管|然后指定的筛选并对模型。<span>这将调用用AngularJS滤波器指令和它提供所要查找的文字模式。</span>NG的重复将显示基于过滤器的返回结果。走在前面，在文本框中输入的东西，看到的结果<span>自动更新</span><span>。</span>\r\n\r\n过滤器就这么简单! 这个<strong>AngularJS</strong> 教程不会介绍到更高级的过滤器或自定义过滤器,但是后面会有更多<a title="Angularjs教程" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/"><strong>AngularJS 教程</strong></a>!\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">ANGULARJS显示隐藏</h2>\r\n<strong>AngularJS </strong>这部分教程<span class="high-light-bg">要看你如何隐藏和显示元件。</span>我们要继续使用人阵列作为我们的数据集但我们需要添加一些额外的数据允许我们表明ng-show和ng-hide。更新你的maincontroller.js<span>文件如下</span>：\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n  $scope.people = [\r\n        {\r\n            id: 0,\r\n            name: ''Leon'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 1,\r\n            name: ''Chris'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Indie'',\r\n                ''Drumstep'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 2,\r\n            name: ''Harry'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Thrash Metal'',\r\n                ''Heavy Metal''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: false\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 3,\r\n            name: ''Allyce'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Pop'',\r\n                ''RnB'',\r\n                ''Hip Hop''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        }\r\n    ];\r\n});\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<span>你可以看到，我们已经添加了一个动态的标签，每个人，与设置为false，国旗的唯一的人是哈利。</span>表明ng-hide和ng-show，添加一个额外的<span>联合的命令</span><span>你的</span><span>HTML</span>列表如下<span>：</span>\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n这将简单将数据输出两次。现在我们将开始使用<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> 和<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> 基于我们创建的活动标签的值. 更新你的HTML如下:\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-show=''person.live == true''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-hide=''person.live == false''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n正如我们所见 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> 和 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> 使用完全相同的方式, <span class="high-light-bg">除非他们是彼此相反的（明显的）。</span>在上面的例子中，我们引用的个人变量声明为NG的重复和公正的评价是否活的属性是真还是假部分。如果你打开这个例子在您的浏览器中你会看到哈利不再出现在任一列表<span>。</span>\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/filter2.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Filtering" width="575" height="331" /></div>\r\n<span>用AngularJS隐藏或显示一个元素是多么容易</span>地\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">ANGULARJS事件</h2>\r\n<span>这种快速的用AngularJS教程的最后一部分将在事件。</span><span class="high-light-bg">事件一直JavaScript框架如jQuery，这并没有改变用AngularJS一个强大的功能。</span>说明我们要添加另一个输入和一个<span>按钮，</span><span>我们的</span>HTML<span>如下</span><span>：</span>\r\n<pre><code>\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-show=''person.live == true''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''newPerson'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;button ng-click=''addNew()''&gt;Add&lt;/button&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n我们只是添加了一个 <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">newPerson</span> 的输入框和一个按钮用ng-click绑定了addNew的响应函数. <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span>文件更新如下:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n  $scope.people = [\r\n        {\r\n            id: 0,\r\n            name: ''Leon'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 1,\r\n            name: ''Chris'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Indie'',\r\n                ''Drumstep'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 2,\r\n            name: ''Harry'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Thrash Metal'',\r\n                ''Heavy Metal''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: false\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 3,\r\n            name: ''Allyce'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Pop'',\r\n                ''RnB'',\r\n                ''Hip Hop''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        }\r\n    ];\r\n    $scope.newPerson = null;\r\n    $scope.addNew = function() {\r\n        if ($scope.newPerson != null &amp;&amp; $scope.newPerson != "") {\r\n            $scope.people.push({\r\n                id: $scope.people.length,\r\n                name: $scope.newPerson,\r\n                live: true,\r\n                music: []\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n});\r\n</code></pre>\r\n上述JS表明我们已经宣布新的$scope变量和一个$scope的方法AddNew的按钮<span>。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>在新的功能，我们只是检查，新的值不为空或空，然后添加一个新的对象的数组的末尾的人。</span><span>这是一个很简单的例子，如何可以用在用AngularJS单击事件。</span><span>有许多可用的</span><span>如</span>NG变化，NG检查，NG的选择，但这不会用AngularJS教程等进入更多的细节，<span>你</span><span>可以在</span><span>用AngularJS</span><span>如果你想了解更多</span><span>。</span>\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">总结</h2>\r\n<span>这种快速的用AngularJS教程应该给你足够的了解如何用AngularJS作品在一个很高的水平，它是能够。</span><span>你现在应该能够</span><span>继续</span>开始<span>创建您自己的</span><span>用AngularJS</span><span>应用学习</span><span>更多</span><span>。</span>\r\n\r\n<span>在学习的同时，我发现文档不是很大，它采取了很多的实验和找工作的例子用AngularJS。</span><span>我希望本教程让你起来，用AngularJS约30分钟的运行。</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n备注：简单百度翻译了一下\r\n\r\n</div>', '30分钟带你了解angularjs', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-07 23:17:22', '2014-12-07 15:17:22', '', 12, 'http://ngionic.com/2014/12/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(13, 1, '2014-12-07 21:42:38', '2014-12-07 13:42:38', '<div class="entry-intro">\r\n<div class="entry-excerpt">这篇<a title="2014年Angularjs学习资源精选" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/" target="_blank"><em><strong>AngularJS</strong></em></a> 教程会让你通过一个精简指令集和补习，包你30分钟内全部用AngularJS 知识。在这短暂而详细的用AngularJS 教程你将能够快速创建功能强大的、直观的Web应用程序。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="entry-content">\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">开始 <a title="2014年Angularjs学习资源精选" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/" target="_blank"><em><strong>AngularJS</strong></em></a></h2>\r\n先做准备工作建一个 <strong>AngularJS</strong>的静态页面. 命名为index.html代码如下:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n     &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在我们可以通过操作静态页面打开 <a href="http://angularjs.org/" target="_blank">http://angularjs.org/</a> 并复制最新<strong>AngularJS </strong>库的CDN.或者下载一份最新的到本地将他引入到你的index.html的头部中\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n     &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n     &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n     &lt;div id=''content''&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\nOk, now we have a HTML page and <strong>AngularJS</strong> included ready for use, lets move on.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">SETTING UP THE PAGE FOR ANGULARJS</h2>\r\nThere are a few things we need to do to tell <strong>AngularJS</strong> that it needs to render this page as an application. As this is a quick <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong>we will not be going into detail as to how you can create multi-application and multi-controller pages, we are just going to declare this page as an <strong>AngularJS</strong> app, and its really simple!\r\n\r\nSimply add <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-app=”MyTutorialApp”</span> to the content DIV as follows:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp''&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nNow we have told <strong>AngularJS</strong> that this DIV is an angular application, we need to declare which controller to use, as follows:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span> is just a name that I made up, controllers should be named with some meaning and as this controller will be handling most of the application, main seems quite appropriate. Some would argue that this still is not enough definition, for this tutorial though, its fine! Ok, we now know what anything within the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">#content</span> DIV will be controlled by the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span>, but where is this controller? We need to make it! Within the same directory as you index.html file we need to create a JS file called <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">app.js</span> and it should look like the following:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\nvar app = angular.module(''MyTutorialApp'',[]);\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nAll this file is doing is creating an <strong>AngularJS</strong> app called <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MyTutorialApp</span> and assigning it to the app variable which we can use later on. Now we need to create another file called, <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> and it should look as follows:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n		\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nThis is assigning a controller called, <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span> to the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MyTutorialApp</span> application. All this JavaScript could be placed within the same JavaScript file but it is good practice to separate them out to keep your code maintainable and easier to understand. Just remember that <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">app.js</span> needs to be included before <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span>. Lets do this now and include both files within out HTML so we can get started!\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nWe now have the page and <strong>AngularJS</strong> application ready, lets move on with this <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong>.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">UNDERSTANDING THE SCOPE</h2>\r\nWhen we created the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> code you may have noticed the $scope variable that we added as a parameter to the controller function. This is where we will assign all our controller variables which will then make them available within the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">#content</span> DIV in the HTML page. Take a look at the following example to understand this concept. Declare a <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">$scope</span> variable within the controller:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n    $scope.understand = "I now understand how the scope works!";\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nIn the above code we simply created a scope variable and assigned a string to it. Now we can access this within our HTML.\r\n<pre class="prettyprint"><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n			{{understand}}\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nWithin the above HTML we wrap the <strong>understand</strong> variable with <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">{{}}</span> so <strong>AngularJS</strong> knows it needs to do something with it. Note how we have not added the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">$scope.</span> to the front of the variable name. If you now view your index.html file within a browser, you should see the following:\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-670" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/understandscope.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Scope" width="578" height="274" /></div>\r\nNow you should understand what scope variables are and that they are also available within the HTML by wrapping then with {{}}. You should also understand that the scope is available only to that controller so you could not access the “knowledge” variable from outside the #content DIV, unless the same controller was defined.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">UNDERSTANDING BINDING</h2>\r\nSo, it was pretty cool that we can declare a scope variable within the JS and instantly access it within the HTML, but <strong>AngularJS</strong> can offer so much more. Data binding is a large topic but this <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> will cover the most important parts to ensure you understand what is possible and allow you to investigate further on your own (Or wait for more <strong>AngularJS tutorials</strong> :D). To understand this concept, lets declare a scope variable which will act as a model. Modify <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> to look as below:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n     $scope.inputValue = "";\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nNow lets add some additional HTML to our page:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n		&lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''inputValue'' /&gt;\r\n		{{inputValue}}\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nAbove we have added a simple text input and used <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-model</span> to bind it to the scope variable <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">inputValue</span>. Note how we did not wrap it in <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">{{}}</span> as it is being used within a <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-*</span> tag. Additionally we are outputting the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">inputValue</span> scope variable onto the page as we did before with the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">understand</span> variable.\r\n\r\nBy doing all this we have bound the input value to the variable. This means that whenever the input value changes, the variable will update to match this. Open the page in a web browser and start typing within the input box. You should see something like the following:\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-671" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/binding1.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Binding" width="492" height="198" /></div>\r\nAs you type the scope variable updates with the new input value and then as you are outputting the variable on this screen this also updates too, magic! Now you have a way of keeping various elements and values in sync within the page. Lets move on to a more complex example to get a better understanding of what is possible. Update <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> to look like below:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n	$scope.selectedPerson = 0;\r\n	$scope.selectedGenre = null;\r\n	$scope.people = [\r\n		{\r\n			id: 0,\r\n			name: ''Leon'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Rock'',\r\n				''Metal'',\r\n				''Dubstep'',\r\n				''Electro''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 1,\r\n			name: ''Chris'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Indie'',\r\n				''Drumstep'',\r\n				''Dubstep'',\r\n				''Electro''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 2,\r\n			name: ''Harry'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Rock'',\r\n				''Metal'',\r\n				''Thrash Metal'',\r\n				''Heavy Metal''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 3,\r\n			name: ''Allyce'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Pop'',\r\n				''RnB'',\r\n				''Hip Hop''\r\n			]\r\n		}\r\n	];\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nWe have declared three scope variables, <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">selectedPerson</span> is going to hold the object of the selected person. <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">selectedGenre</span> is going to hold the string value of the selected genre. Finally we have an array of objects which are people with their own musics tastes. What we are going to hope to achieve is have two select drop downs. One you will be able to select the person, then the other, thanks to binding will automatically update to allow you to select that persons music genres. Lets add this HTML elements to our page:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n		&lt;select ng-model=''selectedPerson'' ng-options=''obj.name for obj in people''&gt;&lt;/select&gt;\r\n		&lt;select ng-model=''selectedGenre''&gt;\r\n			&lt;option ng-repeat=''label in people[selectedPerson.id].music''&gt;{{label}}&lt;/option&gt;\r\n		&lt;/select&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nThere are some new bits here so lets look at them in detail. Firstly we have a select input with <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-options</span> tag. This allows us to populate this select input with the values from the people scope variable, using the name attribute within the person objects as the label, making the actual value of the select option, the object itself. This <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> is not going to go into great details of <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-options</span> you can read more about that <a href="http://docs.angularjs.org/api/ng.directive:select" target="_blank">here</a>. Play around and see what is possible.\r\n\r\nThe next select input is populate itself a different way, for demonstrative purposes. “ng-repeat” in my mind is one of the most powerful features of <strong>AngularJS</strong>. <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span> simple allows you to replicate HTML elements based on an array or set of objects. In the HTML above “ng-repeat” will create an option for each of the music genres within the people.music array based on the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">selectedPersons</span> ID value which is determined by the first selected box as we have declared <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">selectedPerson</span> as its model as we did before with the input.\r\n<p class="alert-info"><strong>Note:</strong> <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span> can be used on any HTML element, once more, go and experiment!</p>\r\nWithin the ng-reapted option tag we have then put <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">{{label}}</span> between the opening and closing option tags, this is to output the label that we declared within the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span>. Open it within the browser, select a person and you should see something like the following:\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-672" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/binding2.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Binding" width="492" height="229" /></div>\r\nSo you can see that as we have used the model to bind the selects value we can then use this anywhere where the same scope is available to update other elements!\r\n<p class="alert-info"><strong>Note:</strong> people[selectedPerson.id].music is only working as the people ID#s are the same as the array indexes. This would not be an ideal solution in a real world situation as you cannot guarantee that the people ID#s will match the array index.</p>\r\nYou should now have a good understanding of what binding is about and what is possible. We have also looked at ng-repeat and ng-options two powerful features of <strong>AngularJS</strong>.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">FILTERING DATA WITH ANGULARJS</h2>\r\nThis <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> is now going to cover filtering as this is another super powerful <strong>AngularJS</strong> feature. We are going to reuse the people scope array from the previous section and create a simple interface that will allow us to search for the peoples names and output the results to a page. Update your HTML as follows:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nHere we have added a text input and provided it with a model <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">searchText</span> we don’t need to declare this physically in the scope within <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span>. We have also created a un-ordered list and added an <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span> to the list element which will create a list element for every person within the people array which we created in the last section. If you open this in your browser now, you should see the following:\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-673" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/filter1.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Filtering" width="575" height="232" /></div>\r\nYou will be able to see all the names of the people within the people array displayed within a list under the search input. Looking back at the HTML we can see some additional code within the ng-repeat. We have added a pipe | and then specified filter and then the model. This will call the <strong>AngularJS</strong> filter directive and provide it with the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">searchText</span> model. The <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span> will then display results based on what the filter returns. Go ahead and type something within the text box and see the results automatically update.\r\n\r\nFiltering is as simple as that! This <strong>AngularJS</strong> tutorial will not cover more advance filtering or custom filters, but keep tuned for more<strong>AngularJS tutorials</strong> that will!\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">HIDING AND SHOWING ELEMENTS WITH ANGULARJS</h2>\r\nThis section of the <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> is going to look at how you can hide and show elements. We are going to continue using the people array as our data-set but we need to add some additional data to allow us to demonstrate <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> and <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span>. Update your <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> file as follows:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n  $scope.people = [\r\n        {\r\n            id: 0,\r\n            name: ''Leon'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 1,\r\n            name: ''Chris'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Indie'',\r\n                ''Drumstep'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 2,\r\n            name: ''Harry'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Thrash Metal'',\r\n                ''Heavy Metal''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: false\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 3,\r\n            name: ''Allyce'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Pop'',\r\n                ''RnB'',\r\n                ''Hip Hop''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        }\r\n    ];\r\n});\r\n</code></pre>\r\nYou can see that we have added a live flag to each of the people, the only person with the flag set to false is Harry. To demonstrate both <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> and <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span>, add an additional un-ordered list to your HTML as follows:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\nThis will simply output the same data twice. Now we are going to use <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> and <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> to conditionally hide list elements based on the live flag we have just created. Update your HTML to match the below code:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-show=''person.live == true''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-hide=''person.live == false''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\nAs you can see <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> and <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> are used in exactly the same way, except they are the opposite of each other (obviously). In the above example we are referencing the person variable which is declared as part of the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span> and just evaluation whether its live attribute is true or false. If you open this example in your browser you will see that <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">Harry</span> no longer appears in either list.\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/filter2.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Filtering" width="575" height="331" /></div>\r\nAnd that is how easy it is to conditionally hide or show an element with <strong>AngularJS</strong>.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">EVENTS WITH ANGULARJS</h2>\r\nThe final part of this quick <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> will look at events. Events have always been a powerful feature of JavaScript frameworks such as jQuery and this has not changed with <strong>AngularJS</strong>. To demonstrate this we are going to add another input and a button to our HTML as below:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-show=''person.live == true''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''newPerson'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;button ng-click=''addNew()''&gt;Add&lt;/button&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\nWe have just added an input with a model <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">newPerson</span> and a button with <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-click</span> which will call a function called <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">addNew</span>. We now need to update our <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> file as follows:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n  $scope.people = [\r\n        {\r\n            id: 0,\r\n            name: ''Leon'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 1,\r\n            name: ''Chris'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Indie'',\r\n                ''Drumstep'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 2,\r\n            name: ''Harry'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Thrash Metal'',\r\n                ''Heavy Metal''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: false\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 3,\r\n            name: ''Allyce'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Pop'',\r\n                ''RnB'',\r\n                ''Hip Hop''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        }\r\n    ];\r\n    $scope.newPerson = null;\r\n    $scope.addNew = function() {\r\n        if ($scope.newPerson != null &amp;&amp; $scope.newPerson != "") {\r\n            $scope.people.push({\r\n                id: $scope.people.length,\r\n                name: $scope.newPerson,\r\n                live: true,\r\n                music: []\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n});\r\n</code></pre>\r\nThe above JS shows that we have declared the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">newPerson</span> scope variable and a scope function <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">addNew</span> which will be called on the button click thanks to the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-click</span> we added to the button.\r\n\r\nWithin the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">addNew</span> function we are just checking that the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">newPerson</span> value is not null or empty and then added a new object to the end of the people array. This is a very simple example of how a click event can be used within <strong>AngularJS</strong>. There are many more available such as <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-change</span>, <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-checked</span>, <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-select</span>, etc but this <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> will not go into any more detail, you can head over to <a href="http://docs.angularjs.org/api/" target="_blank">AngularJS</a> if you want to learn more.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">CONCLUSION</h2>\r\nThis quick <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> should have given you enough to understand how <strong>AngularJS</strong> works on a high level and what it is capable of. You should now be able to go ahead and starting creating your own <strong>AngularJS</strong> applications to learn more.\r\n\r\nWhile learning <strong>AngularJS</strong> I found that the documentation was not great and it took a lot of experimentation and searching to find working examples. I recommend you get a book or two, I used <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1449344852/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1449344852&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=revwebdes-20">AngularJS</a> as a reference book, it has some good examples. If your in the US buy it <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1449344852/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1449344852&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=revwebdes-20">here</a>, if you in the UK buy it <a href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/product/1449344852/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1634&amp;creative=6738&amp;creativeASIN=1449344852&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=revwebdes-21">here</a>. I hope this tutorial got you up and running with <strong>AngularJS</strong> in about 30 minutes. Please give me your feedback via the comments box.\r\n\r\n</div>', '30分钟带你了解angularjs', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-07 21:42:38', '2014-12-07 13:42:38', '', 12, 'http://ngionic.com/2014/12/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(14, 1, '2014-12-07 21:49:41', '2014-12-07 13:49:41', '<div class="entry-intro">\r\n<div class="entry-excerpt">这篇<a title="2014年Angularjs学习资源精选" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/" target="_blank"><em><strong>AngularJS</strong></em></a> 教程会让你通过一个精简指令集和补习，包你30分钟内全部用AngularJS 知识。在这短暂而详细的用AngularJS 教程你将能够快速创建功能强大的、直观的Web应用程序。</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="entry-content">\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">开始 <a title="2014年Angularjs学习资源精选" href="http://ngionic.com/category/angularjs/" target="_blank"><em><strong>AngularJS</strong></em></a></h2>\r\n先做准备工作建一个 <strong>AngularJS</strong>的静态页面. 命名为index.html代码如下:\r\n<pre><code style="color: green;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n     &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n现在我们可以通过操作静态页面打开 <a href="http://angularjs.org/" target="_blank">http://angularjs.org/</a> 并复制最新<strong>AngularJS </strong>库的CDN.或者下载一份最新的到本地将他引入到你的index.html的头部中\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n     &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n     &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n     &lt;div id=''content''&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\nOk, now we have a HTML page and <strong>AngularJS</strong> included ready for use, lets move on.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">SETTING UP THE PAGE FOR ANGULARJS</h2>\r\nThere are a few things we need to do to tell <strong>AngularJS</strong> that it needs to render this page as an application. As this is a quick <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong>we will not be going into detail as to how you can create multi-application and multi-controller pages, we are just going to declare this page as an <strong>AngularJS</strong> app, and its really simple!\r\n\r\nSimply add <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-app=”MyTutorialApp”</span> to the content DIV as follows:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp''&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nNow we have told <strong>AngularJS</strong> that this DIV is an angular application, we need to declare which controller to use, as follows:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\n<span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span> is just a name that I made up, controllers should be named with some meaning and as this controller will be handling most of the application, main seems quite appropriate. Some would argue that this still is not enough definition, for this tutorial though, its fine! Ok, we now know what anything within the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">#content</span> DIV will be controlled by the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span>, but where is this controller? We need to make it! Within the same directory as you index.html file we need to create a JS file called <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">app.js</span> and it should look like the following:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\nvar app = angular.module(''MyTutorialApp'',[]);\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nAll this file is doing is creating an <strong>AngularJS</strong> app called <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MyTutorialApp</span> and assigning it to the app variable which we can use later on. Now we need to create another file called, <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> and it should look as follows:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n		\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nThis is assigning a controller called, <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MainController</span> to the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">MyTutorialApp</span> application. All this JavaScript could be placed within the same JavaScript file but it is good practice to separate them out to keep your code maintainable and easier to understand. Just remember that <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">app.js</span> needs to be included before <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span>. Lets do this now and include both files within out HTML so we can get started!\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nWe now have the page and <strong>AngularJS</strong> application ready, lets move on with this <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong>.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">UNDERSTANDING THE SCOPE</h2>\r\nWhen we created the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> code you may have noticed the $scope variable that we added as a parameter to the controller function. This is where we will assign all our controller variables which will then make them available within the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">#content</span> DIV in the HTML page. Take a look at the following example to understand this concept. Declare a <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">$scope</span> variable within the controller:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n    $scope.understand = "I now understand how the scope works!";\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nIn the above code we simply created a scope variable and assigned a string to it. Now we can access this within our HTML.\r\n<pre class="prettyprint"><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n			{{understand}}\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nWithin the above HTML we wrap the <strong>understand</strong> variable with <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">{{}}</span> so <strong>AngularJS</strong> knows it needs to do something with it. Note how we have not added the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">$scope.</span> to the front of the variable name. If you now view your index.html file within a browser, you should see the following:\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-670" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/understandscope.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Scope" width="578" height="274" /></div>\r\nNow you should understand what scope variables are and that they are also available within the HTML by wrapping then with {{}}. You should also understand that the scope is available only to that controller so you could not access the “knowledge” variable from outside the #content DIV, unless the same controller was defined.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">UNDERSTANDING BINDING</h2>\r\nSo, it was pretty cool that we can declare a scope variable within the JS and instantly access it within the HTML, but <strong>AngularJS</strong> can offer so much more. Data binding is a large topic but this <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> will cover the most important parts to ensure you understand what is possible and allow you to investigate further on your own (Or wait for more <strong>AngularJS tutorials</strong> :D). To understand this concept, lets declare a scope variable which will act as a model. Modify <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> to look as below:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n     $scope.inputValue = "";\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nNow lets add some additional HTML to our page:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n		&lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''inputValue'' /&gt;\r\n		{{inputValue}}\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nAbove we have added a simple text input and used <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-model</span> to bind it to the scope variable <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">inputValue</span>. Note how we did not wrap it in <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">{{}}</span> as it is being used within a <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-*</span> tag. Additionally we are outputting the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">inputValue</span> scope variable onto the page as we did before with the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">understand</span> variable.\r\n\r\nBy doing all this we have bound the input value to the variable. This means that whenever the input value changes, the variable will update to match this. Open the page in a web browser and start typing within the input box. You should see something like the following:\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-671" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/binding1.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Binding" width="492" height="198" /></div>\r\nAs you type the scope variable updates with the new input value and then as you are outputting the variable on this screen this also updates too, magic! Now you have a way of keeping various elements and values in sync within the page. Lets move on to a more complex example to get a better understanding of what is possible. Update <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> to look like below:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n	$scope.selectedPerson = 0;\r\n	$scope.selectedGenre = null;\r\n	$scope.people = [\r\n		{\r\n			id: 0,\r\n			name: ''Leon'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Rock'',\r\n				''Metal'',\r\n				''Dubstep'',\r\n				''Electro''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 1,\r\n			name: ''Chris'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Indie'',\r\n				''Drumstep'',\r\n				''Dubstep'',\r\n				''Electro''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 2,\r\n			name: ''Harry'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Rock'',\r\n				''Metal'',\r\n				''Thrash Metal'',\r\n				''Heavy Metal''\r\n			]\r\n		},\r\n		{\r\n			id: 3,\r\n			name: ''Allyce'',\r\n			music: [\r\n				''Pop'',\r\n				''RnB'',\r\n				''Hip Hop''\r\n			]\r\n		}\r\n	];\r\n});\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nWe have declared three scope variables, <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">selectedPerson</span> is going to hold the object of the selected person. <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">selectedGenre</span> is going to hold the string value of the selected genre. Finally we have an array of objects which are people with their own musics tastes. What we are going to hope to achieve is have two select drop downs. One you will be able to select the person, then the other, thanks to binding will automatically update to allow you to select that persons music genres. Lets add this HTML elements to our page:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n	&lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n		&lt;select ng-model=''selectedPerson'' ng-options=''obj.name for obj in people''&gt;&lt;/select&gt;\r\n		&lt;select ng-model=''selectedGenre''&gt;\r\n			&lt;option ng-repeat=''label in people[selectedPerson.id].music''&gt;{{label}}&lt;/option&gt;\r\n		&lt;/select&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nThere are some new bits here so lets look at them in detail. Firstly we have a select input with <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-options</span> tag. This allows us to populate this select input with the values from the people scope variable, using the name attribute within the person objects as the label, making the actual value of the select option, the object itself. This <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> is not going to go into great details of <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-options</span> you can read more about that <a href="http://docs.angularjs.org/api/ng.directive:select" target="_blank">here</a>. Play around and see what is possible.\r\n\r\nThe next select input is populate itself a different way, for demonstrative purposes. “ng-repeat” in my mind is one of the most powerful features of <strong>AngularJS</strong>. <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span> simple allows you to replicate HTML elements based on an array or set of objects. In the HTML above “ng-repeat” will create an option for each of the music genres within the people.music array based on the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">selectedPersons</span> ID value which is determined by the first selected box as we have declared <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">selectedPerson</span> as its model as we did before with the input.\r\n<p class="alert-info"><strong>Note:</strong> <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span> can be used on any HTML element, once more, go and experiment!</p>\r\nWithin the ng-reapted option tag we have then put <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">{{label}}</span> between the opening and closing option tags, this is to output the label that we declared within the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span>. Open it within the browser, select a person and you should see something like the following:\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-672" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/binding2.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Binding" width="492" height="229" /></div>\r\nSo you can see that as we have used the model to bind the selects value we can then use this anywhere where the same scope is available to update other elements!\r\n<p class="alert-info"><strong>Note:</strong> people[selectedPerson.id].music is only working as the people ID#s are the same as the array indexes. This would not be an ideal solution in a real world situation as you cannot guarantee that the people ID#s will match the array index.</p>\r\nYou should now have a good understanding of what binding is about and what is possible. We have also looked at ng-repeat and ng-options two powerful features of <strong>AngularJS</strong>.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">FILTERING DATA WITH ANGULARJS</h2>\r\nThis <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> is now going to cover filtering as this is another super powerful <strong>AngularJS</strong> feature. We are going to reuse the people scope array from the previous section and create a simple interface that will allow us to search for the peoples names and output the results to a page. Update your HTML as follows:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code>\r\n</pre>\r\nHere we have added a text input and provided it with a model <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">searchText</span> we don’t need to declare this physically in the scope within <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span>. We have also created a un-ordered list and added an <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span> to the list element which will create a list element for every person within the people array which we created in the last section. If you open this in your browser now, you should see the following:\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-673" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/filter1.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Filtering" width="575" height="232" /></div>\r\nYou will be able to see all the names of the people within the people array displayed within a list under the search input. Looking back at the HTML we can see some additional code within the ng-repeat. We have added a pipe | and then specified filter and then the model. This will call the <strong>AngularJS</strong> filter directive and provide it with the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">searchText</span> model. The <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span> will then display results based on what the filter returns. Go ahead and type something within the text box and see the results automatically update.\r\n\r\nFiltering is as simple as that! This <strong>AngularJS</strong> tutorial will not cover more advance filtering or custom filters, but keep tuned for more<strong>AngularJS tutorials</strong> that will!\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">HIDING AND SHOWING ELEMENTS WITH ANGULARJS</h2>\r\nThis section of the <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> is going to look at how you can hide and show elements. We are going to continue using the people array as our data-set but we need to add some additional data to allow us to demonstrate <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> and <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span>. Update your <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> file as follows:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n  $scope.people = [\r\n        {\r\n            id: 0,\r\n            name: ''Leon'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 1,\r\n            name: ''Chris'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Indie'',\r\n                ''Drumstep'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 2,\r\n            name: ''Harry'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Thrash Metal'',\r\n                ''Heavy Metal''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: false\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 3,\r\n            name: ''Allyce'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Pop'',\r\n                ''RnB'',\r\n                ''Hip Hop''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        }\r\n    ];\r\n});\r\n</code></pre>\r\nYou can see that we have added a live flag to each of the people, the only person with the flag set to false is Harry. To demonstrate both <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> and <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span>, add an additional un-ordered list to your HTML as follows:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\nThis will simply output the same data twice. Now we are going to use <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> and <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> to conditionally hide list elements based on the live flag we have just created. Update your HTML to match the below code:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-show=''person.live == true''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-hide=''person.live == false''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\nAs you can see <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-show</span> and <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-hide</span> are used in exactly the same way, except they are the opposite of each other (obviously). In the above example we are referencing the person variable which is declared as part of the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-repeat</span> and just evaluation whether its live attribute is true or false. If you open this example in your browser you will see that <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">Harry</span> no longer appears in either list.\r\n<div class="figure"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-674" src="http://www.revillwebdesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/filter2.png" alt="AngularJS Tutorial - Filtering" width="575" height="331" /></div>\r\nAnd that is how easy it is to conditionally hide or show an element with <strong>AngularJS</strong>.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">EVENTS WITH ANGULARJS</h2>\r\nThe final part of this quick <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> will look at events. Events have always been a powerful feature of JavaScript frameworks such as jQuery and this has not changed with <strong>AngularJS</strong>. To demonstrate this we are going to add another input and a button to our HTML as below:\r\n<pre><code style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n  &lt;title&gt;Learning AngularJS&lt;/title&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/angularjs/1.0.7/angular.min.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="app.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n    &lt;script src="maincontroller.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n    &lt;div id=''content'' ng-app=''MyTutorialApp'' ng-controller=''MainController''&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''searchText'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;ul&gt;\r\n            &lt;li ng-repeat=''person in people | filter:searchText'' ng-show=''person.live == true''&gt;#{{person.id}} {{person.name}}&lt;/li&gt;\r\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n        &lt;input type=''text'' ng-model=''newPerson'' /&gt;\r\n        &lt;button ng-click=''addNew()''&gt;Add&lt;/button&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\nWe have just added an input with a model <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">newPerson</span> and a button with <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-click</span> which will call a function called <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">addNew</span>. We now need to update our <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">maincontroller.js</span> file as follows:\r\n<pre><code class="javascript" style="color: #f8f8f2;">\r\napp.controller("MainController", function($scope){\r\n  $scope.people = [\r\n        {\r\n            id: 0,\r\n            name: ''Leon'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 1,\r\n            name: ''Chris'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Indie'',\r\n                ''Drumstep'',\r\n                ''Dubstep'',\r\n                ''Electro''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 2,\r\n            name: ''Harry'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Rock'',\r\n                ''Metal'',\r\n                ''Thrash Metal'',\r\n                ''Heavy Metal''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: false\r\n        },\r\n        {\r\n            id: 3,\r\n            name: ''Allyce'',\r\n            music: [\r\n                ''Pop'',\r\n                ''RnB'',\r\n                ''Hip Hop''\r\n            ],\r\n            live: true\r\n        }\r\n    ];\r\n    $scope.newPerson = null;\r\n    $scope.addNew = function() {\r\n        if ($scope.newPerson != null &amp;&amp; $scope.newPerson != "") {\r\n            $scope.people.push({\r\n                id: $scope.people.length,\r\n                name: $scope.newPerson,\r\n                live: true,\r\n                music: []\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n});\r\n</code></pre>\r\nThe above JS shows that we have declared the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">newPerson</span> scope variable and a scope function <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">addNew</span> which will be called on the button click thanks to the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-click</span> we added to the button.\r\n\r\nWithin the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">addNew</span> function we are just checking that the <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">newPerson</span> value is not null or empty and then added a new object to the end of the people array. This is a very simple example of how a click event can be used within <strong>AngularJS</strong>. There are many more available such as <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-change</span>, <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-checked</span>, <span class="inline-code" style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666;">ng-select</span>, etc but this <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> will not go into any more detail, you can head over to <a href="http://docs.angularjs.org/api/" target="_blank">AngularJS</a> if you want to learn more.\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: 300; color: #373737;">CONCLUSION</h2>\r\nThis quick <strong>AngularJS tutorial</strong> should have given you enough to understand how <strong>AngularJS</strong> works on a high level and what it is capable of. You should now be able to go ahead and starting creating your own <strong>AngularJS</strong> applications to learn more.\r\n\r\nWhile learning <strong>AngularJS</strong> I found that the documentation was not great and it took a lot of experimentation and searching to find working examples. I recommend you get a book or two, I used <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1449344852/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1449344852&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=revwebdes-20">AngularJS</a> as a reference book, it has some good examples. If your in the US buy it <a href="http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1449344852/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1449344852&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=revwebdes-20">here</a>, if you in the UK buy it <a href="http://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/product/1449344852/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1634&amp;creative=6738&amp;creativeASIN=1449344852&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=revwebdes-21">here</a>. I hope this tutorial got you up and running with <strong>AngularJS</strong> in about 30 minutes. Please give me your feedback via the comments box.\r\n\r\n</div>', '30分钟带你了解angularjs', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-07 21:49:41', '2014-12-07 13:49:41', '', 12, 'http://ngionic.com/2014/12/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
